info.author: Paul A. Lambert
info.description:
CryptoPy is a pure python implmentation of cryptographic algorithms and
applications. The algorithms are developed for readability more than speed. The
collection now includes IEEE 802.11i specific algorithms that generated the test
vectors for 802.11i.
